Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.81,White font,,0,0,0,,Switzerland, the land of historical fine arts and Alps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:22.04,White font,,0,0,0,,How is the scary story from this country going be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When you're ready, miss Haruka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.45,Christine,,0,0,0,,What I'm about to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.09,Christine,,0,0,0,,Is a story about a church \Non a certain Swiss town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:40.63,Christine,,0,0,0,,There was a big, big \Nclock tower in this church
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.50,Christine,,0,0,0,,And beneath it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.13,Christine,,0,0,0,,Lied the remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:48.10,Christine,,0,0,0,,Of the XIV century mayor of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.47,Christine,,0,0,0,,Said to be killed by a deadly poison
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:03:39.76,teGAKI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fscx38.25\fscy100\3c&H000000&\4c&HF47410&\4a&HFF&\pos(259.875,948)}The{\fs30} {\fs60}mayor{\fs30} {\fs60}under{\fs30} {\fs60}the{\fs30} {\fs60}tower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:55.96,Christine,,0,0,0,,Time passed, and in the XX century
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.41,Christine,,0,0,0,,A group of scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.12,Christine,,0,0,0,,Unearthed the mayor's corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.02,Christine,,0,0,0,,In order to perform an autopsy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.56,Christine,,0,0,0,,The examination went on for roughly one week
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.19,Christine,,0,0,0,,But when they were about to bury his bones back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.43,Christine,,0,0,0,,For some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.63,Christine,,0,0,0,,The skull was nowhere to be found
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:22.70,Christine,,0,0,0,,In the end, they decided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:27.68,Christine,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}To deposit the corpse as it was, without the skull
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.28,Christine,,0,0,0,,Then, few weeks later,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.78,Christine,,0,0,0,,Near the clock tower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:38.29,Christine,,0,0,0,,Two siblings were playing soccer together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.79,Christine,,0,0,0,,At one point, the ball started rolling away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.93,Christine,,0,0,0,,Until it reached a grassy spot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.10,Christine,,0,0,0,,Right under the clock tower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.17,Christine,,0,0,0,,And in that grassy spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:54.87,Christine,,0,0,0,,There was a man on all fours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.87,Christine,,0,0,0,,In desperate search for something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.98,Christine,,0,0,0,,When the big brother hurried up to get the ball back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.75,Christine,,0,0,0,,The figure of that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.85,Christine,,0,0,0,,Already disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.72,Christine,,0,0,0,,The brother, who found it eerie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.72,Christine,,0,0,0,,Hurried up and picked the ball up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.88,Christine,,0,0,0,,And quickly run back to his sister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.86,Christine,,0,0,0,,But then, she noticed something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.76,Christine,,0,0,0,,And shouted as if in pure agony:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.44,Christine,,0,0,0,,"NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.77,Christine,,0,0,0,,The brother, surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.87,Christine,,0,0,0,,Looked down to the soccer ball he was holding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.57,Christine,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.31,Christine,,0,0,0,,He realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.08,Christine,,0,0,0,,The ball have turned...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.85,Christine,,0,0,0,,...Into an old-looking skull
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is this... famous in Switzerland?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.13,Christine,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's one of the most famous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,To be honest, by the moment the soccer ball came in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.73,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I thought myself, "that must be the skull"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It kinda leaked out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:55.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:04:00.20,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It may change to a different path from there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Me too, I was like "it just can't be that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.97,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,But it was     {\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HBB1906&} - Just as we pictured it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.41,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just like that
