Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:53.68,White font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs105\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\c&H22F2FA&\3c&H3F3B3C&\pos(369.563,1017)}G{\fs63\3c&H22F2FA&\c&H000000&}irolamo Panzetta
