Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:50.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So, our representative for Italy is mr. Girolamo Panzetta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.53,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Please, take a seat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When you're ready, Girolamo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:04.38,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,My story is... of course, happened in Italy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.22,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,It was... from when I was around 20 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.49,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make a new product
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.82,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,A perfume
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.93,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,So, the city of perfumes is in France
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.69,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,On the southern side of it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:20.76,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,In Provence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.06,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,It's a place called Grasse
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.37,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,In that place there are a lot of small factories
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.97,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And you can sort of create your own perfume there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.91,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,But the town I was in was Naples
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.71,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,So I had to go from Naples to Genova
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.01,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,By train
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.81,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And from Genova
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:41.85,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I had to take a car and travel along the coast
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.85,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And then I had to get inside a mountain road
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:48.19,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,Just when I entered this mountain road
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.79,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,There was a small station, and before it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.29,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,There was a little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.73,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,She was hitch-hiking, doing the autostop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:01.27,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,She was wearing a white dress,\Nher shoes were white too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:15:28.93,teGAKI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fscx38.25\fscy100\3c&H000000&\4c&HF47410&\4a&HFF&\pos(182.25,948)}The{\fs30} {\fs60}white{\fs30} {\fs60}girl
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.10,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,She had a big bag, like a Chanel bag
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.94,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And her skin was pale white too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.64,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I asked her where she was headed to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.75,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And it was exactly the same\N town I was headed to, Grasse
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:17.75,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,As soon as she got inside my car
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.62,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I noticed that her smell was really similar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:24.53,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,To the perfume I wanted to create myself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.76,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I thought "that must be fate"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:31.76,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,So, we got in the car and\N went running through the mountain road
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.90,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,But the girl kept on saying \N"take it easy, go slower"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.74,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,You know there are lots of cabins here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.65,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,We were going straight \Nbut then she was like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.88,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,"Stop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.68,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,So I stepped on the brake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.18,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I was surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.41,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,When I turned towards her
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.62,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,She was gone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.29,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I was confused, but when I looked ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.99,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,Right before the cabin I noticed there were the remains
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.79,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,Of an incident
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.53,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,There were victims
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:02.06,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,She told me to stop and so I did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.23,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I wasn't involved in that incident
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.69,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,So, I had goosebumps
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.69,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And when I looked over
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.44,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,The place lit by the lights
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:13.94,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,Which was on the roadside
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:16.54,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,I noticed there were lots of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.25,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And beside them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.99,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,There were pictures of those\N who died in such incident
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.82,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,And one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.15,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,Was the girl who was with me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.86,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,That was my story
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There are similar japanese stories      {\c&H079D12&}- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:35.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was kinda japanese-styled    {\c&HC23FAA&} - It was, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Its style was similar
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.00,Housei,,0,0,0,,Was this your experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.97,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,It was     {\c&HC23FAA&} - A real experience? Woah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:44.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The most amazing thing about this story
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is the fact it involved the smell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.38,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It was stylish
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.08,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's kinda... italian
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I mean, the whole episode
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was about a perfume
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,With that on mind, he may be lying, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:00.45,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,It's not--- I mean, I always \Nget that when I tell this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even his horror stories are fashionable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.59,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.99,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,You know, that girl had a name
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Which was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.55,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,It was Paolo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.30,Girolamo,,0,0,0,,This was a lie, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.10,Hamada,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.47,Endo,,0,0,0,,He did it right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.47,Housei,,0,0,0,,It was a joke, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:21.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He really loves to say such hard-to-get jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.78,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"Hard to get"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.01,Endo,,0,0,0,,I don't know when he's joking!   \N{\c&H079D12&} - I got it thanks to Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.35,White font,,0,0,0,,Coming next
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.38,White font,,0,0,0,,A scary story from Nigeria, Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:37.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Our representative from Nigeria is mr Bobby Ologun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:34.90,White font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,200)\fs105\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3F3B3C&\pos(410.063,1008)}B{\fs63\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}obby Ologun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:38.94,White font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs105\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\c&H22F2FA&\3c&H3F3B3C&\pos(410.063,1008)}B{\fs63\3c&H22F2FA&\c&H000000&}obby Ologun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:38.94,White font,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fscx39\fscy83\pos(590.625,870)}Nigeria representative
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:38.29,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:46.41,teGAKI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fscx48.75\fscy98\3c&H161D60&\3a&H00&\4c&HF47410&\4a&HFF&\pos(452.25,900)}Nigeria
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.90,White font,,0,0,0,,What will be the scary story from Nigeria,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:45.97,White font,,0,0,0,,A place where believe \Nin black magic to this day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.87,Bobby,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.21,Bobby,,0,0,0,,A story I heard from my mama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.71,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's a cursed tale
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.05,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Of a village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.95,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Still existing to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.12,Bobby,,0,0,0,,In this village, from old times
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.12,Bobby,,0,0,0,,There was a food's name
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:19:24.64,teGAKI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fscx38.25\fscy100\3c&H000000&\4c&HF47410&\4a&HFF&\pos(195.75,948)}The{\fs30} {\fs60}cursed{\fs30} {\fs60}village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.76,Bobby,,0,0,0,,You couldn't say out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:15.16,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Because by saying its name
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:17.46,Bobby,,0,0,0,,They said
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:22.17,Bobby,,0,0,0,,A 2-headed 6-legged huge monster
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.71,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Called {\i1}[some nigerian name]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.71,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Would surely shows itself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.18,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's a gigantic boar
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:29.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.91,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The legend says
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:36.18,Bobby,,0,0,0,,That if it shows up,\N someone from the village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:40.12,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Will die from a mysterious \Ndeath within 7 days
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.46,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The village still can't say
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:47.63,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The name of this food to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.13,Bobby,,0,0,0,,But then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.87,Bobby,,0,0,0,,A certain group of magicians
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.60,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Tried to solve this mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.94,Bobby,,0,0,0,,And so they came to the village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.64,Bobby,,0,0,0,,To put an end to the curse
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.45,Bobby,,0,0,0,,In order to solve this mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.13,Bobby,,0,0,0,,They danced... exorcism dance\N all over the village
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.50,Bobby,,0,0,0,,They started to dance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.93,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.65,Bobby,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:16.29,Bobby,,0,0,0,,While saying that forbidden name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.79,Bobby,,0,0,0,,But each time they said it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:24.80,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The 2-headed, 6-legged \N[monster name] appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.77,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Each time he shouted
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:34.37,Bobby,,0,0,0,,A mysterious death will occur
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.72,Bobby,,0,0,0,,One day passed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.58,Bobby,,0,0,0,,And then people died
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.58,Bobby,,0,0,0,,After two days
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.45,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Again, 10 other people died
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.69,Bobby,,0,0,0,,When six days passed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:48.32,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The 200 magicians
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.69,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Were reduced to 7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.93,Bobby,,0,0,0,,And so, the people from the village
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.18,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Became frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:57.10,Bobby,,0,0,0,,And expelled the \Nremaining 7 magicians
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.67,Bobby,,0,0,0,,From then on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.03,Bobby,,0,0,0,,If someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.50,Bobby,,0,0,0,,...Would end up \Nentering this village
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.21,Bobby,,0,0,0,,They would surely be \Ncaught by the villagers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.38,Bobby,,0,0,0,,And they would \Nbeat them repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:12.11,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Before they would \Nsay that food's name
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:15.18,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The name of that food
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:20.18,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\fs37.5\pos(565.313,54)\fscx72.75\fscy133}note: "inya" is based off what I could hear. Not sure about its actual name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.52,Bobby,,0,0,0,,...Was "inya"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:23.26,Bobby,,0,0,0,,[yoruba language]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.64,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Sorry but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I got it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.63,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Its second half was horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.47,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what it was about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:35.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,I listened to it though
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.55,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He sounded more like an old lady\N from Okinawa on the second half
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.98,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.98,Bobby,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534.938,936)}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.58,Bobby,,0,0,0,,In this village
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.88,Bobby,,0,0,0,,There's a food\N name you can't say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that part is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.25,Bobby,,0,0,0,,By the moment you say it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.30,Bobby,,0,0,0,,The [monster name] will\Nemerge from the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:55.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's the first time we heard "ground"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.00,Bobby,,0,0,0,,But it's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,942)\clip(398,762,697,912)}It's not!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,942)\clip(317,915,683,966)}It's not!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.57,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's how it goes for this story\N{\c&H007FFF&}- It wasn't obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Which food is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:02.86,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's inya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:03.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.80,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Inya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:05.57,Endo,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.63,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Inya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:07.47,Endo,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.24,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Inya\N{\c&H007FFF&}- Inya?   {\c&H079D12&} - Inya..?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:10.10,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Inya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:10.94,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:11.65,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's inya!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.11,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah but what?\N{\c&HC23FAA&}- We got that, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:18.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,What is it like?  {\c&HBB1906&} - What kind of food is it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.15,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What kind of food is it?\N{\c&H0F6D9B&}- It's inya!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.45,Endo,,0,0,0,,But what is an "inya"?\N{\c&HC23FAA&}- Explain us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.85,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's food\N{\c&H007FFF&}- Is it a fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is it a fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.09,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Is it something like a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.53,Bobby,,0,0,0,,It's like a mochi made from sweet potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.03,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1065)\clip(288,867,800,1038)}So you knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,1065)\clip(380,1038,756,1068)}So you knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Just say it if you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:37.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Just say that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.03,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.39,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.07,Bobby,,0,0,0,,Everyone in my country eats it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And how do you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:46.78,Bobby,,0,0,0,,With tomatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:50.44,Bobby,,0,0,0,,You stuff em all inside a roasted capybara
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.01,Bobby,,0,0,0,,And then you gulp it down
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.46,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's an impressive food!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.46,Housei,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!\N{\c&HC23FAA&}- It is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:57.82,Housei,,0,0,0,,Capybara!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's not normal at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's not ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's the worst!\N{\c&H0F6D9B&}- It's not!
